author: Joe Murphy
title: Iowa Map Game: Here are the results
text:
Iowa, Iowa Iowa. What are we going to to about you. You're rectangle-ish, you're midwestern, and most people don't know where you are.
Tuesday we asked readers if they could place Iowa, given just a topographic map of North America . 47.4% located Iowa successfully, fewer than any other state we've asked people about ( Kansas stands at 69.4% correct , Colorado at 60.8% , Tennessee is close at 47.9% and 55.6% got Nebraska right ).
